  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413970/extras/43ffad8b4706c914bda60dd022e5e385.avif?t=1749034333\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413970/extras/f95230ba62972394fc39238de3eb7e32.poster.avif?t=1749034333\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413970/extras/f95230ba62972394fc39238de3eb7e32.webm?t=1749034333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413970/extras/31f4ae1f90c2937134246b40ba8cac56.avif?t=1749034333\" width=620 height=474 /></span>Five years after a world war, Ryunosuke travels to the country of Stivale for a change of pace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While there, he bumps into a fox girl named Serena, and before he knows it, he’s brawling with the police. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrust into the middle of her conflict, Ryunosuke decides to have some fun and accompany Serena on her mission to take down the mafia and reform the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-Based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li></ul>",
